is limited primarily because epinephrine can:$$,
    $$medium$$,
    $$approved$$,
    NULL,
    $$Malamed, Handbook of Local Anesthesia — vasoconstrictors and cardiovascular disease$$,
    now()
  )
  on conflict (slug) do update set
