    (qid, $$B$$, $$deliver a sustained-release systemic antibiotic to the surgical site$$, false, $$Standard periodontal dressings are not drug-delivery devices; they contain no systemic antibiotic.$$, 1),
    (qid, $$C$$, $$permanently splint the adjacent teeth together$$, false, $$Dressings are removed within about a week and are not a permanent splinting solution; long-term splinting uses separate fixed appliances.$$, 2),
