residual 5-mm pockets. Compared with a low-risk, non-smoking patient who has no residual deep
pockets, this patient's periodontal maintenance recall interval should be:$$,
    $$medium$$,
    $$approved$$,
    NULL,
    $$Newman & Carranza, Clinical Periodontology — risk-based supportive periodontal therapy intervals$$,
    now()
  )
  on conflict (slug) do update set
    taxonomy_id = excluded.taxonomy_id,
    format = excluded.format,
    stem = excluded.stem,
    difficulty = excluded.difficulty,
