    $$When scheduling and treating a patient with well-controlled type 2 diabetes, the dental hygienist
should generally:$$,
    $$medium$$,
    $$approved$$,
    NULL,
    $$Wilkins, Clinical Practice of the Dental Hygienist — the patient with diabetes$$,
    now()
  )
  on conflict (slug) do update set
