    $$The most important message to give a patient newly diagnosed with plaque-induced gingivitis is that
the condition is:$$,
    $$easy$$,
    $$approved$$,
    NULL,
    $$Darby & Walsh, Dental Hygiene: Theory and Practice — patient education, gingivitis$$,
    now()
  )
  on conflict (slug) do update set
