cardiovascular disease?$$, $$About 0.04 mg total — roughly two cartridges of 1:100,000 epinephrine — combined with slow
injection and routine aspiration, rather than avoiding vasoconstrictor entirely.$$, $$approved$$, $$Malamed, Handbook of Local Anesthesia — vasoconstrictor dosing in cardiovascular disease$$, now())
